item.title: How do i make a himatchi server?
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

you mean hamachi get it here www.hamachi.cc then when finished downloading open it up and click the tirangle button then once you select create new network then put the name and pass in and click ok then you should see your ip at the top of the screen once someone joins your network then give them your ip and port to sign in.to join other peoples servers go into the triangle button again and click join network and put their network name and pass in and check the owners ip and find there port and click log in

hope this helps

         blitz
